"title": "3020: Holy Spirit, joy of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3020: holy spirit, joy of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit brings joy to believers, giving them an inner contentment and happiness which is not dependent upon external circumstances.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit enables the Messiah to bring joy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2-Isa9:3\">ISA 9:2–9:3</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit gives joy</h2>\n<h3>To those anticipating Jesus Christ's birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:41-Luke1:45\">LUK 1:41–1:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67-Luke1:68\">LUK 1:67–1:68</a></p>\n<h3>To Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:9\">HEB 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>To disciples even in the face of opposition</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13-1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's fruit includes joy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></p>\n<h2>Evidence of the Holy Spirit's work prompts believers to rejoice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15-Acts11:18\">ACT 11:15–11:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23-Acts11:24\">ACT 11:23–11:24</a></p>",
